                                                              throws IOException,
                                                                     ApiException
        Retrieve segment assignments by customer ID.
        Parameters:
        customerIdType - Type of ID used to identify customer (e.g. email, cookie, and phone). (required)
        customerId - Primary identifier of the customer to query for segment assignments. (required)
        pageSize - Number of entities to return. Maximum of 200. (optional)
        after - The cursor that points to the end of the set of entities that has been returned. (optional)
        segmentScope - Scope to filter on. If not specified, both session-scoped and customer-scoped assignments are returned. (optional)
        assignmentState - Assignment state to filter on. If not specified, both assigned and unassigned assignments are returned. (optional)
        Returns:
        SegmentAssignmentListing
        Throws:
